# Diamond Advance — Hybrid Checkoff Lending Platform

**Hybrid (C) model**: Primary repayment via employer checkoff deduction, fallback via M-Pesa STK push. Disbursement via M-Pesa B2C. Built as Vite + vanilla JS SPA with localStorage simulation.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Frontend simulation** — All data persists in localStorage. M-Pesa, USSD, and checkoff flows are realistically simulated but don't hit real APIs. Architecture is designed for easy backend integration later.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Branding**: "Diamond Advance" under Diamond FSA. Dark theme with green (#00c853) + gold (#ffc107) fintech palette.

