### 2. Three Portals

#### Borrower Portal
| Page | Key Features |
|------|-------------|
| Landing | Hero "Get Paid Before Payday", features, how-it-works |
| Register | 4-step KYC: Personal → Employment → Contact → OTP |
| Login | Phone + OTP simulation |
| Dashboard | Limit, active loan, next deduction, credit score, quick actions |
| Apply | Eligibility check → amount slider + term → offer review → disbursement animation |
| Loan Details | Repayment schedule table, status badges, circular progress |
| Repay | STK push sim + Paybill info (123456) |
| Profile | View/edit info, loan history, logout |

#### Employer Portal (HR/Payroll)
| Page | Key Features |
|------|-------------|
| Login | Email + password |
| Dashboard | Active employees, pending deductions, remittance status |
| Upload | CSV deduction upload (period, staff_no, id_no, phone, amount) |
| Deductions | Staff deductions list with search |
| Remittance | Summary, reconciliation report, dispute flagging |

#### Admin Dashboard
| Page | Key Features |
|------|-------------|
| Login | Hardcoded admin@diamond.co.ke / admin123 |
| Overview | KPIs (disbursed, active, default rate), charts, recent apps |
| Loans | Filterable table, approve/reject, detail modal |
| Users | Search, detail modal (KYC, history, score), suspend |
| Employers | Registry, A/B/C tiers, checkoff status, add/edit |
| Reports | Collections, default aging, employer reconciliation, CSV export |

---

### 3. Loan Rules (Hybrid Flat-Fee)

| Tenor | Fee Rate | Example (KES 10,000) |
|-------|----------|---------------------|
| 7 days | 6% | Repay 10,600 |
| 14 days | 8% | Repay 10,800 |
| 30 days | 10% | Repay 11,000 |
| 60 days | 15% | Repay 11,500 |

- **Max loan**: 30-40% of net salary
- **One active loan** at a time
- **Grace period**: 3 days
- **Penalty**: Fixed fee, capped at 10% of principal
- **Primary**: Employer checkoff deduction
- **Fallback**: M-Pesa STK push on due date

---

### 4. USSD Simulator

Full menu tree under `*384*55#` with Diamond FSA branding:
- Register → ID → DOB → Employer → Staff No → Accept T&Cs
- Check Limit → Shows eligible amount
- Apply → Amount → Term → Disbursement method → Offer → PIN confirm
- My Loan → Balance, due date, statement
- Repay → STK push or Paybill details
- Help → FAQs, agent, terms

Feature phone styled UI: green/black, monospace, 160-char screens, keypad input.

---

### 5. Eligibility Scoring

| Factor | Weight |
|--------|--------|
| Employment verified | 25% |
| Salary consistency (3mo) | 20% |
| Net pay threshold (≥20k) | 15% |
| Employer risk band (A/B/C) | 20% |
| Existing loan status | 10% |
| Phone + ID match | 5% |
| Account age | 5% |

Score ≥ 60 → Eligible. Max amount = score% × 40% of net salary.

